  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Bonbibi.DialogueLine
  speaker: 6
  text: My side of the forest is not infinite. The creatures here don't belong to
    anyone. They simply live here. Every time someone like that man decides the rules
    are for other people, they pay the cost, not him!
